    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You mentioned the benefits are \"undeniable,\" but I've heard pretty intense pushback from people living in the outer boroughs. It seems like a lot of people see it as a regressive tax that just makes it harder for people who don't have a choice but to drive to get to work. How do you address that specific criticism?",
